(5336, 'en', 'mail', 'phpfox', '2.0.0alpha1', 'setting_show_core_mail_folders_item_count', '<title>Show inbox, sentbox and deletebox item count</title><info>If enabled will display the mail count totals in each folder, i.e.:\r\n\r\ninbox (2)\r\nsentbox (6)\r\ndelete (10)</info>', '<title>Show inbox, sentbox and deletebox item count</title><info>If enabled will display the mail count totals in each folder, i.e.:\r\n\r\ninbox (2)\r\nsentbox (6)\r\ndelete (10)</info>', 1233234365),
